'''费萨拉巴德'''（[[乌尔都语|乌尔都语]]：'''{{lang|ur|فیصل آباد}}'''），旧名'''莱亚尔普尔'''，是[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[旁遮普省|旁遮普省]]的一座城市，現為巴基斯坦第三大城市及旁遮普省第二大城市，人口超過300萬人。

费萨拉巴德是[[英屬印度|英屬印度]]最早規劃的城市之一，現今已發展成為巴基斯坦的纺织工业中心，另外由於位於旁遮普的地理中心位置，也是一座铁路、公路枢纽，被稱為『巴基斯坦[[曼徹斯特|曼徹斯特]]』<ref name="uaf.edu.pk">{{cite report |date=2005 |title=International Conference on Soil Sustainability and Food Security |url=http://uaf.edu.pk/downloads/2nd_path/Brochure_SSFS_2015.pdf |publisher=University of Agriculture, Faisalabad |access-date=7 June 2016 |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226015428/http://uaf.edu.pk/error.html?aspxerrorpath=%2Fdownloads%2F2nd_path%2FBrochure_SSFS_2015.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Jaffrelot 2002 57">{{cite book |page=57 |title=Pakistan: Nationalism Without A Nation |first=Christophe |last=Jaffrelot |authorlink=Christophe Jaffrelot |publisher=Zed Books |year=2002 |isbn=978-1-84277-117-4 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=I2avL3aZzSEC&pg=PA57 |access-date=2020-08-19 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109203538/https://books.google.com/books?id=I2avL3aZzSEC&pg=PA57 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==城市規劃==
[[File:Clocktower_Faisalabad,_Panorama.jpg|thumb]]
市中心的規劃始於英國統治期間，[[鐘樓_(費薩拉巴德)|鐘樓]]為城市的輻輳點，八條道路在該處交會，從空中俯瞰如同[[英國國旗|英國國旗]]。

==工業==
工业以纺织和食品加工为主。市内有大型纺织厂多家，也有中、小型纺织厂和作坊，还有化肥、罐头食品等工厂，郊区为[[棉花|棉花]]和[[小麦|小麦]]主要产区。截至2013年，費薩拉巴德的GDP（PPP）估計為430億美元<ref name=PBIT>{{cite web| url=http://www.pbit.gop.pk/punjab_at_glance| title=Punjab At A Glance| publisher=Punjab Board of Investment & Trade, Government of The Punjab| date=2016| access-date=April 15, 2017| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170416133204/http://www.pbit.gop.pk/punjab_at_glance| archive-date=2017-04-16| dead-url=yes}}</ref>，預計到2025年將達到870億美元<ref name="faisalabad.dc.lhc.gov.pk">{{Cite web |url=http://faisalabad.dc.lhc.gov.pk/PublicPages/HistoryOfDistrict.aspx |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-08-19 |archive-date=2017-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170709065525/http://faisalabad.dc.lhc.gov.pk/PublicPages/HistoryOfDistrict.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==交通==
費薩拉巴德的鐵路、公路和航空交通十分便利。{{link-en|費薩拉巴德國際機場|Faisalabad International Airport}}距離市中心約15公里（9.3英里）<ref name="anna.aero">{{cite web|title=Qatar Airways becomes Faisalabad's second international service|url=http://www.anna.aero/2015/07/17/qatar-airways-becomes-faisalabads-second-international-service/|website=anna.aero|publisher=PPS Publications|accessdate=7 June 2016|date=17 July 2015|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226015503/https://www.anna.aero/2015/07/17/qatar-airways-becomes-faisalabads-second-international-service/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Gulf Air">{{cite web|title=Gulf Air adds Faisalabad and Multan to Pakistan network|url=https://www.gulfair.com/media-centre/press-releases/gulf-air-adds-faisalabad-and-multan-to-pakistan-network|website=www.gulfair.com|publisher=Gulf Air|accessdate=7 June 2016|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226015344/https://www.gulfair.com/media-centre/press-releases/gulf-air-adds-faisalabad-and-multan-to-pakistan-network|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==氣候==
屬亞熱帶大陸性半乾旱氣候，夏熱冬涼，夏季均溫可高達近攝氏40度；年平均降雨量約為615毫米，降雨集中在七月至九月，有時會有致災性大雨<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.urdupoint.com/en/pakistan/urban-flooding-likely-in-various-divisions-t-720528.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-08-19 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109203551/https://www.urdupoint.com/en/pakistan/urban-flooding-likely-in-various-divisions-t-720528.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.samaa.tv/news/2019/07/pdma-warns-of-urban-flooding-in-several-punjab-cities/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-08-19 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109203555/https://www.samaa.tv/news/2019/07/pdma-warns-of-urban-flooding-in-several-punjab-cities/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

